msgstr "ndarray"

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/legendre.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.legendre.legvander:33
msgid ""
"The pseudo-Vandermonde matrix. The shape of the returned matrix is ``x.shape "
"+ (deg + 1,)``, where The last index is the degree of the corresponding "
"Legendre polynomial.  The dtype will be the same as the converted `x`."
msgstr ""
